Awesome battlecry, dope presence in the new movie, and honestly doesn't look cute and all that typical mythical dumb shit. Like in the new movie, the side protagonist calls Zarude "Touchan", possibly considering Zarude to be like a father figure to the boy. It's a straight up Tarzan reference and I love it. Like to be honest, clean man.
